==English==
===[[Etymology]]===
A [[neologism]] derived from [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bill_Napoli State Senator Bill Napoli's (R-SD)] description of an acceptable rape that would merit an exemption from [http://movies.crooksandliars.com/pbs_nh_sd_virgin_exception_060303a.wmv South Dakota's abortion ban]

===Pronunciation===
nA'poli
===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|Napoli||}}

# ''literal'' - To brutalize and rape, "sodomize as bad as you can possibly make it", a young, religious virgin woman who was saving herself for marriage.
# ''literal'' - To sexually and psychologically terrorize a young, religious, virigin woman saving herself for marriage
# ''figurative'' - To '''aggressively''' put someone at a painful and psychological disadvantage or otherwise take brutal advantage of them in an egregious manner. To grill someone or rake them over the coals.

